                    is public, our releases are SHA-256 verified, and our roadmap is shaped by your input.
                </p>
                <p>
                    We don&rsquo;t rely on marketing claims&mdash;we rely on transparency. If you
                    find a bug, report it. If you have an improvement, submit a pull request. The code is open for everyone to see.
